{"tid":2103371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「待FC」戴耀廷：收到消息，頭兩小時近34000人已投票","createTime":"2020-07-11T06:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:20:56.000Z","uid":345458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0d6a833ca1d2e82aa40a03aeb76d5ccb0d2113","tid":2103371,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0c8f17c986395ccca86a12102352681b36b2e8","tid":2103371,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fe2WwHi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffe2WwHi.png&h=580cf546&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ab49ea68f184b0631e0fe42aaa15725eacca578","tid":2103371,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"應該唔止？好多人喎區區都"},{"pid":"488909af681052bccc03ded76fc2ac182a48fc91","tid":2103371,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:59:50.000Z","msg":"34000/250/2=68<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個街站每個鐘要有68人投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70a174118d468d5ca30a0e623d7ee7d234d83b5","tid":2103371,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"【12：30】戴耀廷籲市民踴躍投票　對超10%投票率有信心<br />\n<br />\n主辦初選的港大法律系教授戴耀廷、前議員區諾軒及民主動力召集人趙家賢中午見記者。戴耀廷表示，不評論警方昨日的行動是否打壓，但他笑稱，本來對投票率能超越 10% 信心不大，但經過這幾天反而很有信心，呼籲市民踴躍投票，用真實的聲音對抗政府。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷表示，初選使用的電腦系統是完全獨立，並非存放在民研辦公室內，不過昨日警察調查影響最後準備工作，所以延遲投票。他又稱，早前有人提出投票系統出現的技術問題，目前已基本上解決，今、明兩日都會有技術人員候命，團隊有信心可處理出現的任何技術問題，包括嚴重網絡攻擊。戴耀廷又強調，系統已更改了加密匙，投票過程收集的個人資料亦會在有結果後馬上銷毀，呼籲公眾放心。<br />\n<br />\n戴指，明日的投票時間將恢復正常，由早上 9 時至晚上 9 時；他又表示，希望今日的投票人數可以達到 8.5 萬，即目標投票人數 17 萬的一半。"},{"pid":"eb85df6fa3b42b0c5702a6edcb70e21b451a668c","tid":2103371,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1669940672a6d6ddc73a017444e53755fbf211ac","tid":2103371,"uid":53149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍share"},{"pid":"7f2d52d12a7afb96f1c71d3d12a05d764609b76a","tid":2103371,"uid":28654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}